        <h2>How to Apply This: A Room-by-Room Environment Redesign Protocol</h2>
        <p>The following protocol applies environment design principles systematically across the physical and digital spaces where your habits occur, using the four core mechanisms — default design, cue visibility, friction, and context specificity — to create an environment that produces desired behaviors automatically.</p>

